Author: LikeaPandaButUgly
Text: 105 won’t be enough. You’re ED will come up with more reasons to push off recovering.  Remember, there are options aside from hospitalization and nothing. Like seeing a therapist, going to a dietitian, outpatient programs.

Author: rosepetalmemories
Text: Welcome to the dark side. The scary part about Ed is how addictive it can become. When I'm too low I chug a few ensures untill I'm at a safe weight.
